metadata.name: Limited Cloud Dude #1
metadata.description: There are many clouds in the sky. There are so many of them that someone could live among them! Cloud Dudes is the NFT collection that combines the clouds of Earth and other planets. Each cloud is unique! The Clouds are so light and free. Therefore, each Cloud symbolizes the freedom of life and choice. Life is a beautiful thing not to be missed! And Cloud Dudes are good at it! When you look at the clouds, know that they will also look at you :) Let's go to the World of Clouds! Cloud-Butler will help you! Follow him.
